## When to Use This Agent

Use **Backend Systems Architect Agent** when:
- You need to design a complete system architecture (not just code)
- You're building for scale (10K → 100K → 1M users)
- You need to understand data flows, component boundaries, API contracts
- You want detailed database design with growth planning
- You need production deployment recommendations
- You're starting a new backend system and need an overview

**Deliverables:**
✅ System architecture diagram (visual)  
✅ Component specifications (responsibilities, boundaries)  
✅ Complete data flow documentation (with diagrams)  
✅ API design with OpenAPI spec  
✅ Normalized database schema (with indices)  
✅ Multi-layer caching strategy  
✅ Production-ready implementation code (4-6 modules)  
✅ Scalability analysis (growth projections)  
✅ Deployment & operations guide  

**Don't use this agent for:**
- Implementing code (use implementation_agent)
- Code review (use code_review_agent)
- Refactoring existing systems (use architecture_refactorer_agent)
- Full-stack projects with UI (use autonomous_dev_agent)

